#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:166
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s collects information which identifies, for each page accessed on %(organisation_name)s, the network identity of the machine which has accessed it. We use Google Analytics and in-house software to perform this function."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:172
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s retains this usage information for purposes of network analysis, usage analysis, and research into usage patterns to improve the %(organisation_name)s services. Access to and use of this information is restricted to Google Analytics, %(organisation_name)s management and staff, and to researchers working on %(organisation_name)s projects and subject to an agreement to adhere to these Terms of Use."
