#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:180
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s reserves the right to gather more extensive information than stated above (i) about any attempted access to %(organisation_name)s which raise security issues (and, where necessary, to make disclosures to relevant authorities); and (ii) for network analyses on an occasional basis."
