#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:188
#, python-format
msgid "Personal information contained in %(organisation_name)s databases"
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:192
msgid "Personal information in court cases"
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:194
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s publishes comprehensive collections of court decisions with the consent of the public bodies concerned. The electronic dissemination of judgments is in concordance with the open court principle, instituted to ensure the impartiality and transparency of the judicial process by allowing access to the record of judicial proceedings, including judgments. Therefore, %(organisation_name)s operates on the core principle that all citizens and organisations should be provided with free, unconditional and unrestricted access to basic legal materials."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:203
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s undertakes to monitor and delete from published judgments personal information as directed by law or specific court order. %(organisation_name)s retains the right to remove personal information from judgments at its discretion where this is possible without distorting the meaning and context of the document."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:209
msgid "Personal information in government gazettes"
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:211
msgid "Government gazettes and official journals are official publications of the states that publish them. The law mandates that certain personal information should be made public via the government gazette and government departments place these public notices in the government gazette with the intent of the contents being made accessible to the public."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:218
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s cannot withdraw from circulation, redact or amend the government gazette."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:222
msgid "Automated monitoring"
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:224
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s performs automated monitoring and, where necessary, de-identification of judgments before publication and does not guarantee that all sensitive material has been correctly de-identified."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:230
#, python-format
msgid "Should you have concerns over personal information published on the %(organisation_name)s website, please contact us."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:234
msgid "Your responsible use of personal information"
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:236
#, python-format
msgid "%(organisation_name)s users should note that there are legal limitations on the use, publication and dissemination of some personal information in %(organisation_name)s databases. It is the responsibility of %(organisation_name)s users to comply with the laws of the land."
msgstr ""

#: templates/peachjam/_terms_of_use_content.html:242
msgid "Right to amend these Terms of Use, Copyright and Privacy statements"
